        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3079",
        "content": "It was fun for the young men whose tale is told here to go with the Shell People and assist in spearing fish or drawing them from the river's depths upon rude hooks, and the Shell People did not object, but were rather proud of the attendance of representatives of the hillside aristocracy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3079_164971_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3079/164971/3079_164971_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3079",
        "content": "The morning was one to make men far older than these two most confident and full of life.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3079_164971_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3079/164971/3079_164971_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3079",
        "content": "The mast had already begun to fall and the nuts lay thickly among the leaves.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3079_164971_000005_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3079/164971/3079_164971_000005_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3079",
        "content": "Every morning, and more regularly than it comes now, there was a spread of glistening hoar frost upon the lowlands and the little open lands in the forest and upon every spot not tree protected.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3079_164971_000005_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3079/164971/3079_164971_000005_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3079",
        "content": "It came most strikingly in spring and autumn, and was something wonderful.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
