        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3079",
        "content": "Yard by yard, Ab's mighty strokes brought him nearer the object of his pursuit.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3079_164971_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3079/164971/3079_164971_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3079",
        "content": "She was swimming breast forward, as was he-for that was his only way-she with a dog like paddling stroke, and often she turned her head to look backward at the man.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3079_164971_000015_000003",
